http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgodsmightroleplaytavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=22.topic&index=47>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How did you get your Paladin name?</span><hr size=1> After playing D&amp;D for years, my favorite character I ever made was a character named Kjara (pronounced Kee -ya - rah)<br>
