<br>
Anyway, I started as my first character a Mage. At first it rocked; I felt powerful... Later on I hated everything. I died a lot and grouped with other people. I couldn't tank well or heal other members. I could only cast worthless spells. After lvl 5 or so I deleted him. (created him because I like role-playing a pure caster)<br>
